1. This Chrome extension does not collect any personal data or personally identifiable information from its users. All processing of data occurs locally on your device.
2. We do not gather, store, or transmit your name, email address, Browse history, financial information, health data, or any other information that could be used to identify you.
3. This extension may use Chrome's local storage API to save user preferences and settings directly on your device. This data is not transmitted to our servers and remains entirely under your control.
4. We do not collect any usage statistics or analytical data from our users.
5. We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated 'Effective Date.'
6. If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at bohdanzhyhor@gmail.com.